data.description: This 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1 car garage block home has so much potential. It is located in a quaint and quiet neighborhood sitting on an oversized 1/4 acre lot on a cul-de-sac. You can sit on your screened-in porch and enjoy your morning coffee in the large backyard. There is a shed for storage and a large covered workshop area or whatever your heart desires. No HOA or CDD! It is conveniently located minutes from CR54 and Chancey Rd getting you wherever you need to go in a hurry. Historic downtown Zephyrhills is a 4-minute drive, Florida Hospital Zephyrhills is a 7-minute drive as well as tons of shopping and dining!
